      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="29452563">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Pre_Asura/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u40227066-13.jpg" alt="AsuraHu" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/29452563/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/29452563/" class="">第3页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Pre_Asura/" class=" " title="AsuraHu">AsuraHu</a>
                (忧乐未知,陌阡不识.)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="29452563">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">文明需要独特的社会秩序。为了满足新宫廷和王城所需，统治者不得不想方设法，强迫农民交纳剩余产品。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-11-21 17:13</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                文明需要独特的社会秩序。为了满足新宫廷和王城所需，统治者不得不想方设法，强迫农民交纳剩余产品。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
